---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>

    <section class="min-h-screen py-10 px-5">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">

            <!-- Header -->
            <div class="mb-10">
                <p class="text-red-400 font-bold tracking-widest text-sm uppercase mb-3" data-i18n="about.subtitle">Quién soy</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Bloque principal -->
            <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-[1fr_380px] gap-12 items-start">

                <!-- Texto izquierda -->
                <div>

                    <p class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-black leading-snug mb-10 text-justify text-gray-900 dark:text-white" data-i18n="about.intro">
                        Desde pequeño sentí una gran curiosidad por el mundo tecnológico y desde inicios del 2024 empecé a participar en el desarrollo de software empresarial.
                    </p>

                    <div class="space-y-5 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-lg leading-relaxed text-justify">

                        <p data-i18n="about.p1">
                            Estudio Ingeniería de Software en la Universidad Veracruzana, próximo a egresar en julio de 2026.
                        </p>

                        <p data-i18n="about.p2">
                            He trabajado desarrollando sistemas reales tanto trabajando para empresas como de manera independiente.
                            Lo cual no solo me ha ayudado a aprender sobre el desarrollo del software, sino también del mantenimiento
                            y la administración en ambientes de producción reales.
                        </p>

                        <p data-i18n="about.p3">
                            Creo que el buen software no se trata solo de que funcione, sino de que sea fácil de
                            mantener, agradable de usar y resuelva un problema de verdad.
                        </p>

                    </div>

                    <!-- Stats -->
                    <div class="mt-10 md:mt-18 pt-10 border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 grid grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                        <div>
                            <p class="text-4xl font-black text-gray-900 dark:text-white">2+</p>
                            <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm mt-1" data-i18n="about.stats.years">Años de experiencia</p>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <p class="text-4xl font-black text-gray-900 dark:text-white">4+</p>
                            <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm mt-1" data-i18n="about.stats.projects">Proyectos realizados</p>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <p class="text-4xl font-black text-red-400">UV</p>
                            <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm mt-1" data-i18n="about.stats.university">Universidad Veracruzana</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>

                <!-- Foto + info card -->
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">

                    <div class="relative">
                        <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl dark:shadow-black/30 ring-1 ring-gray-200 dark:ring-gray-700">
                            <img
                                src="/fotos/HenryTraje.png"
                                alt="Henry Enoch"
                                class="w-full h-[420px] object-cover object-top"
                            />
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mt-4 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800/80 rounded-2xl p-5 shadow-sm dark:shadow-black/20 border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 flex flex-col gap-4">

                        <p class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest" data-i18n="about.info.title">Información</p>

                        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">

                            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                                <span class="text-sm text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500" data-i18n="about.info.location">Ubicación</span>
                                <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300" data-i18n="about.info.locationValue">Coatzacoalcos, Ver. 🇲🇽</span>
                            </div>

                            <div class="w-full h-px bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700"></div>

                            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                                <span class="text-sm text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500" data-i18n="about.info.availability">Disponibilidad</span>
                                <span class="text-sm font-medium text-green-500" data-i18n="about.info.availabilityValue">Disponible</span>
                            </div>

                            <div class="w-full h-px bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700"></div>

                            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                                <span class="text-sm text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500" data-i18n="about.info.modality">Modalidad</span>
                                <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300" data-i18n="about.info.modalityValue">Remoto / Presencial</span>
                            </div>

                            <div class="w-full h-px bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700"></div>

                            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                                <span class="text-sm text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500" data-i18n="about.info.focus">Enfoque</span>
                                <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300" data-i18n="about.info.focusValue">Full Stack</span>
                            </div>

                            <div class="w-full h-px bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700"></div>

                            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                                <span class="text-sm text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500" data-i18n="about.info.languages">Idiomas</span>
                                <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300" data-i18n="about.info.languagesValue">Español · Inglés básico</span>
                            </div>

                        </div>

                    </div>

                </div>

            </div>

            <!-- Work style -->
            <div class="mt-12 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">

                <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800/80 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-sm dark:shadow-black/20">
                    <p class="text-3xl mb-4">🎯</p>
                    <h4 class="font-black text-lg mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-white" data-i18n="about.workStyle.results.title">Orientado a resultados</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed text-justify" data-i18n="about.workStyle.results.desc">
                        No me conformo con que algo funcione. Me importa que resuelva bien el problema
                        para el que fue creado y que quien lo use lo sienta así.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800/80 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-sm dark:shadow-black/20">
                    <p class="text-3xl mb-4">⚡</p>
                    <h4 class="font-black text-lg mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-white" data-i18n="about.workStyle.adaptable.title">Rápido y adaptable</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed text-justify" data-i18n="about.workStyle.adaptable.desc">
                        He aprendido que en el desarrollo las cosas cambian seguido: requisitos,
                        tecnologías, prioridades. Me adapto a cualquier tipo de cambios.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800/80 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-sm dark:shadow-black/20">
                    <p class="text-3xl mb-4">🤝</p>
                    <h4 class="font-black text-lg mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-white" data-i18n="about.workStyle.collaborative.title">Colaborativo</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed text-justify" data-i18n="about.workStyle.collaborative.desc">
                        Trabajo bien solo, pero mejor en equipo. Escucho, propongo y no tengo problema
                        en reconocer cuando alguien tiene una mejor idea.
                    </p>
                </div>

            </div>

            <!-- Tecnologías -->
            <div class="mt-16">

                <p class="text-red-400 font-bold tracking-widest text-sm uppercase mb-3" data-i18n="about.techStack.subtitle">Stack tecnológico</p>
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-12 text-gray-900 dark:text-white" data-i18n="about.techStack.title">Tecnologías que manejo</h2>

                <div class="grid grid-cols-3 sm:grid-cols-4 md:grid-cols-6 gap-6">

                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-3 group">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-red-50 dark:group-hover:bg-red-900/30 transition-colors">
                            <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/laravel/laravel-original.svg" class="w-9 h-9" alt="Laravel"/>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Laravel</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-3 group">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-red-50 dark:group-hover:bg-red-900/30 transition-colors">
                            <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/php/php-original.svg" class="w-9 h-9" alt="PHP"/>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">PHP</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-3 group">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-red-50 dark:group-hover:bg-red-900/30 transition-colors">
                            <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/express/express-original.svg" class="w-9 h-9" alt="Express"/>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Express</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-3 group">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-red-50 dark:group-hover:bg-red-900/30 transition-colors">
                            <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/javascript/javascript-original.svg" class="w-9 h-9" alt="JavaScript"/>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">JavaScript</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-3 group">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-red-50 dark:group-hover:bg-red-900/30 transition-colors">
                            <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/mysql/mysql-original.svg" class="w-9 h-9" alt="MySQL"/>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">MySQL</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-3 group">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-red-50 dark:group-hover:bg-red-900/30 transition-colors">
                            <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/mongodb/mongodb-original.svg" class="w-9 h-9" alt="MongoDB"/>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">MongoDB</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-3 group">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-red-50 dark:group-hover:bg-red-900/30 transition-colors">
                            <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/react/react-original.svg" class="w-9 h-9" alt="React"/>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">React</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-3 group">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-red-50 dark:group-hover:bg-red-900/30 transition-colors">
                            <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/astro/astro-original.svg" class="w-9 h-9" alt="Astro"/>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Astro</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-3 group">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-red-50 dark:group-hover:bg-red-900/30 transition-colors">
                            <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/git/git-original.svg" class="w-9 h-9" alt="Git"/>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Git</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-3 group">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-red-50 dark:group-hover:bg-red-900/30 transition-colors">
                            <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/github/github-original.svg" class="w-9 h-9" alt="GitHub"/>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">GitHub</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-3 group">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-red-50 dark:group-hover:bg-red-900/30 transition-colors">
                            <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/docker/docker-original.svg" class="w-9 h-9" alt="Docker"/>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Docker</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-3 group">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-red-50 dark:group-hover:bg-red-900/30 transition-colors">
                            <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/tailwindcss/tailwindcss-original.svg" class="w-9 h-9" alt="Tailwind"/>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Tailwind</p>
                    </div>

                </div>

                <p class="mt-12 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-4xl text-justify mb-8">
                    <span data-i18n="about.techStack.closing">Estas son las tecnologías con las que he estado trabajado y con las que me siento cómodo. Sin embargo, no me cierro a nada, si un proyecto o equipo requiere algo diferente, lo tomo como una oportunidad de seguir creciendo como parte de mi</span>
                    <span class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white font-semibold" data-i18n="about.techStack.closingHighlight">aprendizaje constante.</span>
                </p>

            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

</Layout>
